Name: Advantage Full Doc <55% LVR
ProductDetails: The Pepper Advantage suite is designed for customers who, due to restrictive credit criteria, are unable to meet the lending criteria of banks and mortgage insurers. With Pepper Advantage we assess each borrowers unique circumstances, rather than simply basing our decision on a credit score. Purchase or refinance of owner occupied and investment properties, also includes; unlimited debt consolidation, cash out for acceptable purposes and payment of ATO debts. Minor defaults up to $1,000 accepted. Unlimited defaults > $1,000, registered > 12 months (paid or unpaid). < 1 months mortgage arrears (within last 6 months). Discharged from bankruptcy (1 day accepted)
FeeDetails: Mortgage Risk Fee - 0.65% of amount advanced (0.50% MRF loading for loans >$1m). Title Protection Fee $400. Legal Fees from $440 plus disbursements. Estab Fee includes 1 standard valuation (Approx value $395)
RedrawDetails: MIn manual redraw $1000. Min online redraw $50

SplitDetails: This product has an annual fee which covers the splits at time of application.

Name: Offset Home Loan Package 5 Year Fixed Owner Occupied IO <=70% LVR
ProductDetails: Max LVR 80% for interest only loans. A loan incorporating an offset account, full transactional access and multiple account options. 5 years interest only available. Macquarie Bank offers you a Macquarie Platinum Visa Card as part of the LOC Package. (Approval is subject to Macquarie Card Services credit criteria). Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
RateDetails: Loans >$1m to $2m - LVR can be considered up to a max of 80% on case by case basis depending on borrower circumstances, security location/type and overall strength of the application.
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Ongoing package fee is charged at $124 bi-annually. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300).

Name: Bridging  Loan
ProductDetails: Bridging Loans with No End Debt restricted to existing members only. Fully secured, short term property funding loan for members who wish to sell existing property and who have found a new property to purchase, or are purchasing vacant land where building contract or preliminary costing have been entered into. Allows applicants to go ahead and negotiate a new property purchase before selling their existing property. Separate end debt loan to be established at outset. Proof of Income Compulsory . Proof of Deposit Required. End Debt Scenario required for submission. Serviceability must be demonstrated on End Debt on P&I basis. Bridging portion must be repaid in full when property is sold.
FeeDetails: Additional Valuation $1 million + property/Non-Metro $440.00. Legal fees may apply up to $500. Please refer to BDM for more details.

Name: SuperCredit SMSF AAA IO
ProductDetails: For fully verified AAA borrowers only. If members of the SMSF are not graded AAA, please contact Liberty to provide an indicative quote as reductions to the maximum LVR and loadings to rate and/or fee may apply. Max LVR 80%. Clear credit history or past credit impairment can be considered. Principal & interest, or interest only up to 5 years then P&I.
FeeDetails: Set-up fee: $495 to cover the cost of review of existing SMSF arrangements (if a SMSF is already in place). $695 to meet third party costs associated with the establishment of a new SMSF structure (if a SMSF is not already in place).

Name: Fixed Investment Loan 5 Year Interest In Advance
LenderProductName: Fixed Investment Loan 5 Year Interest In Advance
ProductDetails: Please refer to Westpac for specific lending criteria and repayment options. Additional Fee's may be applicable. Discounts apply - Refer to rate details. Name: Bridging Home Loan
ProductDetails: A Variable rate loan for short-term finance to enable a new property to be purchased prior to an existing property being sold. Up to 90% LVR is available including cap LMI. Max I/O period for O/O home loans available up to 5 years.
RateDetails: Rate: Additional 1% after 3 months.
FeeDetails: Application Fee includes one valuation. Additional Valuation fee may vary dependant on the type of valuation, type of property, location etc. Please refer to your BDM.
InterestCapitalisationDetails: A customer can capitalise the interest on a bridging loan when, based on the loan principal amount only, the LVR is a max of 75%. The progressive draw option is not available where interest cap is selected.
SplitDetails: $600 as Combo Loan (for App. Fee). If post settlement, std. App or Switch Fee applies Refer Lender.

Name: 5 Year Fixed Owner Occupied P&I
ProductDetails: Upon rollover to SVR (at the end of the fixed term) full interest rate set off will apply.95% LVR full doc available. Genuine savings (or equity) of at least 5% must be verified for all new loan applications where the base LVR is >90%.
SplitDetails: No charge at settlement for any splits. Future splits $300 variation fee.

Name: Lite Blue - Clear (75% LVR)
ProductDetails: Designed for self employed individuals, companies and trusts. ABN registered for 12 mths. Require 6 mths BAS or business bank statements or accountants letter. Living expenses must be evidenced by 3 mths personal bank statements. Offers P&I/Interest Only (for 3 or 5 yrs), no LMI, redraw, further advances available, splits available. Cash out up to $200K dependent on credit impairment level. From 1 day discharged bankrupt. Max loan $2.25m subject to Bluestone LVR caps/ASL.
RateDetails: Loading of 0.50% to be applied to rate for Interest Only repayment loans. Large loan rate loading (>$1.5m) 0.50%
FeeDetails: LMP/Risk Fee 1.50% payable at settlement. Title Insurance - <$750k from $350, >$750k quote required. Loan settlement fee $120. Legal fees from $400. No valuation fee <$1m, quote required if >$1m. Max LVR is inclusive of capitalised fees (excluding discharge).
RedrawDetails: $50 if assisted, nil if via internet banking

Living expenses must be evidenced by 3 mths personal bank statements. Offers P&I/Interest Only (for 3 or 5 yrs), no LMI, redraw, further advances available, splits available. Cash out up to $200K dependent on credit impairment level. From 1 day discharged bankrupt. Max loan $2.25m subject to Bluestone LVR caps/ASL.
RateDetails: Loading of 0.50% to be applied to rate for Interest Only repayment loans. Large loan rate loading (>$1.5m) 0.50%
FeeDetails: LMP/Risk Fee 1.50% payable at settlement. Title Insurance - <$750k from $350, >$750k quote required. Loan settlement fee $120. Legal fees from $400. No valuation fee <$1m, quote required if >$1m. Max LVR is inclusive of capitalised fees (excluding discharge).
RedrawDetails: $50 if assisted, nil if via internet banking

The support team will supply a link to the broker for the customer to supply 6 months business and personal bank statements electronically via Proviso and the initial assessment will be completed. If eligible for Prime AAA the broker will contacted to request either 2 quarters BAS or the Liberty Accountants letter. Loan Size Limits <50% $2M, < 65%  $1.5M, <70% $1M, <=80% $750k. Professional Investor Rate Loading (0.75%) plus $995 fee (in addition to the Application fee) applies to any application in the name of a company/trust, or any  investment application where the individual borrower owns =3 properties (includes O/O, investment, commercial and residential and includes the new application).(Owner-occupied individual applicants will not be considered professional investors)
FeeDetails: Valuation Fee of $330 inc GST per security (higher if >$1.5m or regional area). Discharge fees of $395 + legals. Equalisation Fee 0.50%. Title Protection fee $349 per security. Professional Investor Fee $995
RedrawDetails: Fee: $50 subject to approval criteria (min $2000 per draw)

Name: Home Advantage Package 5 Year Fixed Investment P&I
ProductDetails: New lending only. Must hold a Heritage Credit Card, pay annual fee & hold an eligible package home loan with a min of $150k lending to be eligible to receive package benefits.
FeeDetails: Where a valuation is required with one property offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation, if two or more securities are involved, or val. costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Name: Discount Variable Home Loan Investment
ProductDetails: Discount Variable Home Loan available for Investment (I/O max 5yrs). Construction, Land, Refinance and Consolidation purposes.
FeeDetails: Where a valuation is required and only one property is offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation. If two or more securities are involved, or valuation costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150 if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. Guarantor Fee $200
RedrawDetails: Online redraw is free. $20 fee charged for manual redraw
SplitDetails: $0 if pre settlement, if post settlement normal Application Fee applies

Name: Easy Alt Doc <65% LVR
ProductDetails: A near prime home loan for borrowers who have not had any credit impairment or defaults in the last 24 mths. Purchase or refinance of owner occupied Finance is also available for a variety of purposes, including payment of ATO debts, renovations and business use; Minor defaults up to $1,000 accepted, Unlimited defaults and judgements > $1,000, registered >24 mths (paid or unpaid), Discharged from bankruptcy (1 day accepted)
FeeDetails: Establishment Fee ($995), Title Protection Fee ($400) and Legal Fees (from $440) waived. Offer valid until 31/01/2019. Mortgage Risk Fee - 0.65% of amount advanced. Estab Fee includes 1 standard valuation (Approx value $395)

Name: SuperCredit SMSF AAA
ProductDetails: For fully verified AAA borrowers only. If members of the SMSF are not graded AAA, please contact Liberty to provide an indicative quote as reductions to the maximum LVR and loadings to rate and/or fee may apply. Max LVR 80%. Clear credit history or past credit impairment can be considered. Principal & interest, or interest only up to 5 years then P&I.
FeeDetails: Set-up fee: $495 to cover the cost of review of existing SMSF arrangements (if a SMSF is already in place). $695 to meet third party costs associated with the establishment of a new SMSF structure (if a SMSF is not already in place).

Name: Liberty Free Low Doc AAA <60% LVR Owner Occupied P&I
ProductDetails: Max Loan <50% $2M, <65% $1.5M, <70% $1M, <=80% $750k. Max loan against single security $1M. Professional Investor Rate Loading (0.75%) plus $995 fee (in addition to the Application fee) applies to any application in the name of a company/trust, or any  investment application where the individual borrower owns =3 properties (includes O/O, investment, commercial and residential and includes the new application).(Owner-occupied individual applicants will not be considered professional investors).
FeeDetails: Valuation Fee ($330) may be waived (subject to conditional approval) for the first security on all Prime loans excluding those with an LVR = 90% up to $330 (incl GST). Professional Investor Fee $995. Split fee - $0 for loans with =4 splits, $495 for loans with >4 splits

Name: Advantage Portfolio Loan
ProductDetails: Only available for investment or blended investment and owner occupied use. (Not available for owner occupied only) Max LVR capped at 80% for interest only repayments. Although Advantage Pack is only available to personal customers, non personal customers (e.g. Companies, Trusts etc) applying for a standard home loan or a Portfolio Loan are entitled to the Advantage Pack interest rate discounts. All standard fees are payable (eg: est fee)

Name: Standard Variable Housing Loan (Regional Areas excl. Kimberley & Pilbara)
ProductDetails: Max property value $500k. Max loan amount: $475k. Max income levels - Singles: $110,000 p.a., Couples/Families: $135,000 p.a. Requirements: Purchase price: up to $480,000 - Higher of 2% deposit or $2k, $480,001 - $500,000 - 5% deposit. Internet banking only available through Keystart client portal
RateDetails: Product is for Regonal Areas excluding the Kimberley and Pilbara regions.
FeeDetails: Title Search Fee $25.70
RedrawDetails: Fee: $25.30 Details: Min $1K for all purposes

Name: HomeStart Loan
ProductDetails: South Australia Only. $3000 Genuine Savings Required saved over 3 months. Refer to Homestart for valuation fees
FeeDetails: Search Admin Fee $21.75. Valuation Fee at cost (including GST). Loan Provision Charges apply up to $2970 depending on LVR, Construction etc. Refer to lender for details.
RedrawDetails: Manual Redraw Fee $50.00, no online Redraw Fee
EarlyRepayBreakCostDetails: No Defered Establishment Fee applies/ Break Cost: not ascertainable - available upon request to break fixed rate
InterestCapitalisationDetails: If this situation arises the borrower may choose to make voluntary repayments to full or partially negate capitalisation
SplitDetails: $150.Split rate (fixed portion fixed for 1-3 years) - for construction applications available at final drawdown, the fixed rate that applies is the fixed rate applicable on the date of the final drawdown (plus 1% for the first 12 months on LDL)

Name: Advantage Full Doc Plus <55% LVR
ProductDetails: The Pepper Advantage suite is designed for customers who, due to restrictive credit criteria, are unable to meet the lending criteria of banks and mortgage insurers. With Pepper Advantage we assess each borrowers unique circumstances, rather than simply basing our decision on a credit score. Purchase or refinance of owner occupied and investment properties, also includes; unlimited debt consolidation, cash out for acceptable purposes and payment of ATO debts. Minor defaults up to $1,000 accepted. Unlimited defaults > $1,000, registered >12 months (paid or unpaid). Unlimited mortgage arrears (within last 6 months). Unlimited defaults, judgements or writs from 1 credit event <12 months (paid or unpaid). Discharged from bankruptcy (1 day accepted)
FeeDetails: Mortgage Risk Fee - 1.00% of amount advanced (0.50% MRF loading for loans >$1m). Title Protection Fee $400. Legal Fees from $440 plus disbursements. Estab Fee includes 1 standard valuation (Approx value $395)
RedrawDetails: MIn manual redraw $1000. Min online redraw $50

Name: Smooth Home Loan (>80% LVR) IO
ProductDetails: A 'no frills' home loan with an ongoing low variable interest rate. For members who do not require the features of other variable rate home loans such as an offset account. Maximum LVR is inclusive of capitalised LMI & fees. Max 5 years I/O repayments
FeeDetails: Additional Valuation $1 million + property/Non-Metro $440.00. Legal fees may apply up to $500. Please refer to BDM for more details.
EarlyRepayBreakCostDetails: N/A Member can pay out loan at any time without penalty.
SplitDetails: Yes, can split with other Credit Act (CA) loan products. If any portion of the total loan amount is for the purpose of CONSTRUCTION/MAJOR RENOVATION, the loan amount CANNOT be split with a fixed rate loan product or line-of-credit.

Clients that take out a Macquarie Bank Flyer Home Loan Package with a Macquarie Visa Platinum Card and opt in to Qantas Frequent Flyer Rewards, can earn Qantas Points on eligible spend on that credit card. Clients can earn: 10,000 Qantas Points for every $100,000 drawn down at settlement as an introductory gift (calculated to the nearest point); 1,000 Qantas Points each month the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the month; a bonus 25,000 Qantas Points on the third and fifth anniversaries of the loan, calculated from the day of settlement, as long as the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the anniversary month. Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
RateDetails: Loans >$1m to $2m - LVR can be considered up to a max of 80% on case by case basis depending on borrower circumstances, security location/type and overall strength of the application
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300).
SplitDetails: Up to 6 splits post settlement, limited to 2 splits at settlement.

Name: Expect More Home Loan - Fixed 5 Year Owner Occupied
ProductDetails: Available for new purchase/refinance of owner occupied residential property. Metro postcodes max 95% LVR, regional postcodes max 60% LVR (excludes WA, NT and TAS). Name: Liberty Nova Low Doc AAA <60% LVR Owner Occupied P&I
ProductDetails: Nova submissions only require the income declaration of the application form to be completed which forms part of the signed pages. The support team will supply a link to the broker for the customer to supply 6 months business and personal bank statements electronically via Proviso and the initial assessment will be completed. If eligible for Prime AAA the broker will contacted to request either 2 quarters BAS or the Liberty Accountants letter. Loan Size Limits <50% $2M, <65%  $1.5M, <70% $1M, <=85% $750k. Professional Investor Rate Loading (0.75%) plus $995 fee (in addition to the Application fee) applies to any application in the name of a company/trust, or any  investment application where the individual borrower owns =3 properties (includes O/O, investment, commercial and residential and includes the new application).(Owner-occupied individual applicants will not be considered professional investors)
RateDetails: Max loan amount $2m up to 50% LVR, $1.5m up to 60% LVR
FeeDetails: Valuation fee of up to a maximum $330 (inc. GST) will be covered for the first security. Additional valuation expenses may be payable in the instance of securities >$1.5m, in a regional location or for additional securities. Professional Investor Fee $995. Split fee - $0 for loans with =4 splits, $495 for loans with >4 splits
SplitDetails: $0 for loans with =4 splits, $495 for loans with >4 splits

Name: Classic Home Loan
ProductDetails: Available only as Owner Occupied with P&I repayments with max LVR 85% plus LMI for a limited time. Offers a redraw facility and no monthly fees. Min loan $150k. (All members must be an Aus citizen/permanent resident)

Name: Premium Home Loan
ProductDetails: Applications with an LVR exceeding 95% will need to meet the following criteria: All applicants are first home buyers and the max loan size is $600k (plus cap LMI). Applications with an LVR greater than or equal to 90% will be acceptable subject to the RDI being greater than or equal to $1000. Name: Interest Only Variable
ProductDetails: Teachers Mutual Bank provides access to financial products and services for current or retired employees of the Australian education sector or family members of members (ie shareholders) of the Bank (Individuals must be citizens or permanent residents of Australia) Interest only variable loan available to be used for purchase, vacant land, renovations, or any acceptable purpose. This loan is suitable for construction purposes. Max LVR 95% inc LMI for O/O (inc LMI) for Lecturers/Teachers, For all other occupations max 90% LVR plus LMI. Conditions apply.

Name: Standard Variable Owner Occupied
ProductDetails: 95% LVR available for O/O Purchases/Construction, 90% LVR available for Investment. Can change term of loan. 100% offset available.
FeeDetails: $250 Solicitors fee for Trust/Co loans where docs are outsourced. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150) if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. Where a valuation is required with one property offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation, if two or more securities are involved, or valuation costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Guarantor Fee $200
RedrawDetails: Online redraw is free. $20 fee charged for manual redraw
SplitDetails: $0 if pre settlement, if post settlement normal Application Fee applies

Name: Basic Flyer Home Loan 5 Year Fixed Owner Occupied P&I <=70% LVR
ProductDetails: Clients that take out a Macquarie Bank Flyer Home Loan Package with a Macquarie Visa Platinum Card and opt in to Qantas Frequent Flyer Rewards, can earn Qantas Points on eligible spend on that credit card. Clients can earn: 10,000 Qantas Points for every $100,000 drawn down at settlement as an introductory gift (calculated to the nearest point); 1,000 Qantas Points each month the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the month; a bonus 25,000 Qantas Points on the third and fifth anniversaries of the loan, calculated from the day of settlement, as long as the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the anniversary month. Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
RateDetails: Loans >$1m to $2m - LVR can be considered up to a max of 80% on case by case basis depending on circumstances, security location/type and strength of the application. LVR <80% -$1.25m, LVR 80 - 90% - $1.1m, LVR >90% - $850k
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300).
SplitDetails: Up to 6 splits post settlement, limited to 2 splits at settlement.

Name: Offset Flyer Home Loan Package 5 Year Fixed Owner Occupied P&I <=70% LVR
LenderProductName: Offset Flyer Home Loan Package Fixed
ProductDetails: Clients that take out a Macquarie Bank Flyer Home Loan Package with a Macquarie Visa Platinum Card and opt in to Qantas Frequent Flyer Rewards, can earn Qantas Points on eligible spend on that credit card. Clients can earn: 10,000 Qantas Points for every $100,000 drawn down at settlement as an introductory gift (calculated to the nearest point); 1,000 Qantas Points each month the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the month; a bonus 25,000 Qantas Points on the third and fifth anniversaries of the loan, calculated from the day of settlement, as long as the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the anniversary month. Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
RateDetails: Loans >$1m to $2m - LVR can be considered up to a max of 80% on case by case basis depending on borrower circumstances, security location/type and overall strength of the application. (LVR >90% max loan $850k)
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Ongoing package fee is charged at $124 bi-annually. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300).

Clients can earn: 10,000 Qantas Points for every $100,000 drawn down at settlement as an introductory gift (calculated to the nearest point); 1,000 Qantas Points each month the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the month; a bonus 25,000 Qantas Points on the third and fifth anniversaries of the loan, calculated from the day of settlement, as long as the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the anniversary month. Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
RateDetails: Loans >$1m to $2m - LVR can be considered up to a max of 80% on case by case basis depending on borrower circumstances, security location/type and overall strength of the application. (LVR >90% max loan $850k)
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Ongoing package fee is charged at $124 bi-annually. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300).

Name: Discount Variable Home Loan Owner Occupied
ProductDetails: Discount Variable Home Loan available for Owner Occupied with  P&I repayments only.
FeeDetails: Where a valuation is required and only one property is offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation. If two or more securities are involved, or valuation costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150 if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. Guarantor Fee $200

Name: Home Advantage Package Variable $700k+ <80% LVR Investment P&I
ProductDetails: New lending only. Must hold a Heritage Credit Card, pay annual fee & hold an eligible package home loan with a minimum of $150k lending to be eligible to receive package benefits.
RateDetails: 1.60% discount (already included) off the Standard Variable rate.
FeeDetails: Where a valuation is required with one property offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation, if two or more securities are involved, or val. costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150 if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. Guarantor Fee $200
SplitDetails: This product has an annual fee which covers the splits at time of application.

Name: Solutions Plus Owner Occupied $750k+ >90% LVR P&I
LenderProductName: Solutions Plus Owner Occupied Rewards Package
ProductDetails: Available for new owner occupiers with new to bank security. Teachers Mutual Bank provides access to financial products and services for current or retired employees of the Australian education sector or family members of members (ie shareholders) of the Bank (Individuals must be citizens or permanent residents of Australia). Max 95% LVR inc LMI for Lecturers/Teachers. For all other occupations max 90% LVR plus LMI.  Offers a discounted rate for the life of the loan and is only available to eligible members with the Rewards Package. Eligibility includes current everyday account, registered online banking, min deposit of $2k per month and new min loan amount of $150k. Max LVR 95% $ for $ existing mortgage otherwise 90% subject to equity release and debt consolidation limits inc LMI
SplitDetails: Ability to split loan. Min split on variable rate is $25k

Name: Home Advantage Package Living Equity $700k +  Investment
ProductDetails: New lending only.The Home Advantage Living Equity have a tiered interest rate structure based on the total lending in the Investment Home Advantage package suite. IO facility, to a max of 10yrs. Must hold a Heritage Credit Card, pay annual fee & hold an eligible package home loan with a min of $150k lending to be eligible to receive package benefits.
FeeDetails: I/O loans can not be switched or refixed, they need to be rewritten/renegotiated. Where a valuation is required with one property offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation, if two or more securities are involved, or val. costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150 if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. Guarantor Fee $200
SplitDetails: This product has an annual fee which covers the splits at time of application.

Name: 5 Year Fixed Owner Occupied
ProductDetails: I/O not avail on O/O loans.
FeeDetails: Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150 if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. SplitDetails: $0 if pre settlement, if post settlement normal Application Fee applies

The support team will supply a link to the broker for the customer to supply 6 months business and personal bank statements electronically via Proviso and the initial assessment will be completed. If eligible for Prime AAA the broker will contacted to request either 2 quarters BAS or the Liberty Accountants letter. Loan Size Limits <50% $2M, < 65%  $1.5M, <70% $1M, <=80% $750k. Professional Investor Rate Loading (0.75%) plus $995 fee (in addition to the Application fee) applies to any application in the name of a company/trust, or any  investment application where the individual borrower owns =3 properties (includes O/O, investment, commercial and residential and includes the new application).(Owner-occupied individual applicants will not be considered professional investors)
FeeDetails: Valuation Fee of $330 inc GST per security (higher if >$1.5m or regional area). Discharge fees of $395 + legals. Equalisation Fee 1.75%. Title Protection fee $349 per security. Professional Investor Fee $995
RedrawDetails: Fee: $50 subject to approval criteria (min $2000 per draw)

The support team will supply a link to the broker for the customer to supply 6 months business and personal bank statements electronically via Proviso and the initial assessment will be completed. If eligible for Prime AAA the broker will contacted to request either 2 quarters BAS or the Liberty Accountants letter. Loan Size Limits <50% $2M, < 65%  $1.5M, <70% $1M, <=80% $750k. Professional Investor Rate Loading (0.75%) plus $995 fee (in addition to the Application fee) applies to any application in the name of a company/trust, or any  investment application where the individual borrower owns =3 properties (includes O/O, investment, commercial and residential and includes the new application).(Owner-occupied individual applicants will not be considered professional investors)
FeeDetails: Valuation Fee of $330 inc GST per security (higher if >$1.5m or regional area). Discharge fees of $395 + legals. Equalisation Fee 0.50%. Title Protection fee $349 per security. Professional Investor Fee $995
RedrawDetails: Fee: $50 subject to approval criteria (min $2000 per draw)

ProductDetails: Available to owner occupiers or investors for new lending only, >$200k and <80% LVR with P&I repayments. Not available for construction. ProductDetails: Membership is focused on National Fire Services but also includes emergency services such as:Police (State/Federal), SES, Ambulance & Paramedics etc. Family members of members (i.e. shareholders) of the Bank are also eligible for membership (individuals must be citizens or permanent residents of Australia). Max 95% LVR inc LMI for Ambulance Officers/Paramedics, Firefighters, Nurse/Midwife and Police Officers. For all other occupations max 90% LVR plus LMI. Product available for new owner occupiers with new to bank security. Offers a discounted rate for the life of the loan and is only available with the Rewards Package. Eligibility includes current everyday account, registered online banking, min deposit of $2k per month and new min loan amount of $150k. Max LVR 95% $ for $ existing mortgage otherwise 90% subject to equity release and debt consolidation limits inc LMI.
SplitDetails: Ability to split loan. Min split on variable rate is $25k

Name: Liberty Nova Low Doc AAA <60% LVR Owner Occupied IO
ProductDetails: Nova submissions only require the income declaration of the application form to be completed which forms part of the signed pages. The support team will supply a link to the broker for the customer to supply 6 months business and personal bank statements electronically via Proviso and the initial assessment will be completed. If eligible for Prime AAA the broker will contacted to request either 2 quarters BAS or the Liberty Accountants letter. Loan Size Limits <50% $2M, <65%  $1.5M, <70% $1M, <=85% $750k .Professional Investor Rate Loading (0.75%) plus $995 fee (in addition to the Application fee) applies to any application in the name of a company/trust, or any investment application where the individual borrower owns =3 properties (includes O/O, investment, commercial and residential and includes the new application).(Owner-occupied individual applicants will not be considered professional investors).
RateDetails: Max loan amount $2m up to 50% LVR, $1.5m up to 60% LVR.
FeeDetails: Valuation fee of up to a maximum $330 (inc. GST) will be covered for the first security. Additional valuation expenses may be payable in the instance of securities >$1.5m, in a regional location or for additional securities. Professional Investor Fee $995. Split fee - $0 for loans with =4 splits, $495 for loans with >4 splits
SplitDetails: $0 for loans with =4 splits, $495 for loans with >4 splits

Name: Liberty Star AAA 3 Year Fixed <80% LVR Owner Occupied IO
ProductDetails: Designed to suit a broad range of applicants including PAYG and self-employed. Name: Complete Fixed Home Loan 5 Year Owner Occupied IO
ProductDetails: The Complete Package offers a discounted rate Home Loan, Offset Accounts and Credit Card. All products must form part of the bundle. Minimum of $200k in Complete Home Loan Package borrowings (once on the package, the minimum loan size for any additional borrowing is then $20k). At the end of the Fixed Period, this loan reverts to the Complete Variable Home Loan. The discount after the Fixed period is dependant on total Package borrowings and the LVR at the time of application.
FeeDetails: The Complete Home Loan Package will comprise of three products for a fee of $395 per year (Home Loan, Offset and Credit Card)
RedrawDetails:
Redraw surplus repayments available through home loan access. Min $1,000 per transaction - $10 fee. (Fee will only be charged for home loan access requests 
completed at Store). Max 90% LVR after redraw

Name: Home Advantage Package 5 Year Fixed Investment IO
ProductDetails: New lending only. Must hold a Heritage Credit Card, pay annual fee & hold an eligible package home loan with a min of $150k lending to be eligible to receive package benefits. I/O max 5 yrs. I/O loans cannot be switched or refixed, they need to be rewritten/renegotiated
FeeDetails: Where a valuation is required with one property offered as security Heritage will pay for the valuation, if two or more securities are involved, or val. costs exceed $330 (inclusive of GST), the difference is to be borne by the borrower. Heritage Settlement Fee - $150 (per settlement). Agents Settlement Fee ranges between $88 - $260 plus disbursements (per settlement) for CBD settlements, depending on state. Where Heritage engages an agent acting on its behalf, the Agents Settlement Fee will be passed on to the borrower. Legal Fees: Nil with the exception of Trust & Company loans which attract a fee of $250 in addition to the application fee. Collateral Security Fee - $100 ($150 if different state) for each additional unencumbered security. Guarantor Fee $200
EarlyRepayBreakCostDetails: Applies if the fixed term is broken early - economic costs
SplitDetails: This product has an annual fee which covers the splits at time of application.

Name: Basic Flyer Home Loan <70% LVR Owner Occupied P&I
ProductDetails: Clients that take out a Macquarie Bank Flyer Home Loan Package with a Macquarie Visa Platinum Card and opt in to Qantas Frequent Flyer Rewards, can earn Qantas Points on eligible spend on that credit card. Clients can earn: 10,000 Qantas Points for every $100,000 drawn down at settlement as an introductory gift (calculated to the nearest point); 1,000 Qantas Points each month the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the month; a bonus 25,000 Qantas Points on the third and fifth anniversaries of the loan, calculated from the day of settlement, as long as the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the anniversary month. Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300). Construction Admin Fee $999
RedrawDetails: Free via internet and phone banking. $50 manual redraw fee.

Clients can earn: 10,000 Qantas Points for every $100,000 drawn down at settlement as an introductory gift (calculated to the nearest point); 1,000 Qantas Points each month the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the month; a bonus 25,000 Qantas Points on the third and fifth anniversaries of the loan, calculated from the day of settlement, as long as the outstanding loan balance is at least $150,000 on the last business day of the anniversary month. Free access to any domestic ATM (Redi, NAB and BOQ networks). Outside the home network the ATM operator may charge a fee. Client accepts the fee and this is refunded same day
FeeDetails: $0 Application fee. Ongoing package fee is charged at $124 bi-annually. Legal Fees are $363 for standard deals and $484 for complex deals. Additional legal costs to a maximum of $190 paid by MBL. Additional Lenders Legal fees will apply when other costs occur. Valuation fee up to $300 included (at cost for valuations over $300). Construction Admin Fee $999
RedrawDetails: Free via internet, phone banking, chq access.  $50 manual redraw fee.

Name: Back to Basics Better Together Bundle Owner Occupied <90% LVR P&I Special
ProductDetails: New lending only. Min $150k. Max 90% LVR (inc LMI). P&I repayments (interest only considered for construction loans only). Pre-approvals excluded. A Suncorp Everyday Basics account is a mandatory requirement (unless the borrower holds a Suncorp transaction account). Offset account not available. Up to 20% discount on 1st yr premium on Suncorp Home & Contents or Landlord Insurance available. The Suncorp Bank Bundle Special Offer consent form must be submitted to receive discounted rate.
RateDetails: 1.40% reduction already included. Pre-approvals excluded. Application fee waived for loans >$150k, (normally $600). Everyday Basics account must be opened as part of bundle offer (not required if has existing Suncorp transaction account).
FeeDetails: Application fee includes Security Admin & Valuation. (Application fee waived for new loans > $150k, a saving of $600.)
RedrawDetails: $20 Each calendar month your first Online Cashback Fee will be rebated
SplitDetails: 1 split free, 2nd split at additional loan rates.  New Split Loan facilities an Account keeping fee will be charged on both facilities.

Name: Premium Plus Package $150k+ <90% LVR Owner Occupied P&I Special
ProductDetails: The Premium Plus Package Home Loan provides low ongoing variable interest rates. The Premium Plus Package annual fee is added to the loan and receipted at settlement. The fee is built into the monthly repayment and paid off the principal. This reduces the principal by an amount equal to the monthly fee and debited on the anniversary. Annual fee is waived on NPBS value plus credit card, 5% disc on comprehensive car insurance, 10% disc on Home & Contents, Landlord and Travel Insurance, application Fee waived for Personal Loans. New Borrowers min $150k, existing borrowers increase min $150k
RateDetails: Rate available to O/O, new and existing customers, min $150k new borrowings, P&I only.
FeeDetails: First valuation fee is covered. If multiple properties are involved, NPBS will pay for the lower of the valuations. Valuation fee pricing guide, properties valued <$1m fee range is $179-$433 and for properties over $1m the minimum fee is $550. Discharge Fee is $250 plus costs
RedrawDetails: Available via Branch or Online. Registration required for Online ability. No Cost
SplitDetails: No limit on splits. No additional Fees where all borrowers are the same

Name: Premium Plus Package Fixed Rate 5 Year Owner Occupied IO
ProductDetails: The Premium Plus Package Home Loan provides low ongoing variable interest rates. Max I/O term is 5 yrs. Max redraw $25k pa. Free 60 day Rate Lock applied on unconditional approval of loan. The Premium Plus Package annual fee is added to the loan and receipted at settlement. The fee is built into the monthly repayment and paid off the principal. This reduces the principal by an amount equal to the monthly fee and debited on the anniversary. Annual fee is waived on NPBS value plus credit card, 5% disc on comprehensive car insurance, 10% disc on Home & Contents, Landlord and Travel Insurance, application Fee waived for Personal Loans
RateDetails: Rate availabe to O/O new lending only. Existing customers may be eligible if existing loan is O/O and increasing loan by min $150k. Conditions apply
FeeDetails: First valuation fee is covered. If multiple properties are involved, NPBS will pay for the lower of the valuations. Valuation fee pricing guide, properties valued < $1m fee range is $179-$433 and for properties over $1m the minimum fee is $550. Discharge Fee is $250 plus costs
RedrawDetails: Available via Branch or Online. Registration required for Online ability. Limited to $25,000 per calendar year
EarlyRepayBreakCostDetails: Break costs are payable if the loan is paid out during the fixed term
SplitDetails: No limit on splits. No additional Fees where all borrowers are the same

Name: Essential Construction Full Doc <55% LVR
ProductDetails: Purchase of land or property for the primary purpose of constructing up to two residential owner occupied properties or making structural changes to an existing owner occupied property. I/O repayments during construction phase then reverts to P&I. Max loan amt NSW & VIC - 1 property - $1.5m (<80%LVR), $850k (<95%); 2 properties - $1.5m (<85%), $1.2m (<95%). All other States - $800k (<95%). Paid defaults up to $500 may be considered. 5% genuine savings required if LVR >90%.
RateDetails: Interest only repayments during construction phase then reverts to P&I

SplitDetails: Up to 3 splits available post construction (including 100% Offset sub account split)

Name: Premium Plus Package Fixed Rate 5 Year Owner Occupied P&I
ProductDetails: The Premium Plus Package Home Loan provides low ongoing variable interest rates. Max redraw $25k pa. Free 60 day Rate Lock applied on unconditional approval of loan. The Premium Plus Package annual fee is added to the loan and receipted at settlement. The fee is built into the monthly repayment and paid off the principal. This reduces the principal by an amount equal to the monthly fee and debited on the anniversary. Annual fee is waived on NPBS value plus credit card, 5% disc on comprehensive car insurance, 10% disc on Home & Contents, Landlord and Travel Insurance, application Fee waived for Personal Loans
FeeDetails: First valuation fee is covered. If multiple properties are involved, NPBS will pay for the lower of the valuations. Valuation fee pricing guide, properties valued < $1m fee range is $179-$433 and for properties over $1m the minimum fee is $550. Discharge Fee is $250 plus costs
RedrawDetails: Available via Branch or Online. Registration required for Online ability. Limited to $25,000 per calendar year
EarlyRepayBreakCostDetails: Break costs are payable if the loan is paid out during the fixed term
SplitDetails: No limit on splits. No additional Fees where all borrowers are the same
